companyProfile: {'companyDescription': 'NTPC Limited is an India-based power generating company. The Company is primarily involved in the generation and sale of bulk power to State Power Utilities. Its segments include Generation of energy and Others. Its generation of energy segment is engaged in generation and sale of bulk power to state power utilities. Its other segment is focused on providing consultancy, project management and supervision, energy trading, oil & gas exploration, and coal mining. The Company operates a total of 92 power stations across various Indian states, either independently or through its joint ventures (JVs) and subsidiaries.
